</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">다리로 이어지는 신경을 압박하므로 요통뿐 아니라 </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">엉치와</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">다리의 통증</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">땡김</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: ko; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">저림</span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; language: en-US; mso-ascii-font-family: '맑은 고딕'; mso-bidi-font-family: +mn-cs; mso-color-index: 1; mso-font-kerning: 12.0pt\">, </span><span style=\"FONT-FAMILY: '맑은 고딕'; COLOR: black; FONT-SIZE: 12pt; mso-fareast-font-family